## 4. Rules Summary

### DO:
- ✅ Define all typography styles in `lib/typography.ts`
- ✅ Define all user-facing strings in `lib/strings.ts`
- ✅ Use constants for button text, labels, messages
- ✅ Use validation message generators for dynamic messages
- ✅ Prepare for localization by centralizing strings

### DON'T:
- ❌ Hardcode font sizes like `text-[14px]`
- ❌ Hardcode strings like `"Loading..."`
- ❌ Mix typography styles inconsistently
- ❌ Use inline style objects for typography
- ❌ Duplicate strings across components

